abstract: Reports include quarterly earnings from Facebook, Comcast and General Motors, as well as vehicle sales and unemployment numbers for April.
snippet: Reports include quarterly earnings from Facebook, Comcast and General Motors, as well as vehicle sales and unemployment numbers for April.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Data to be released include personal income and spending, pending home sales and the Dallas Fed’s manufacturing activity (Monday); the Standard & Poor’s/Case-Shiller Home Price Index, the Chicago Purchasing Managers’ Index and consumer confidence for April (Tuesday); A.D.P. employment for April, the I.S.M. manufacturing index for April and United States vehicle sales for April (Wednesday); the trade deficit for March and weekly initial jobless claims (Thursday); and unemployment for April (Friday).

headline.main: Economic Reports for the Week Ahead
